+    ${cell(v.streak, '连续天数')}${cell(v.due, '待复习')}${cell(v.mastered, '已掌握')}${cell(v.learned, '学习中')}${cell(v.retention != null ? v.retention + '%' : '—', '回忆达标率')}</div>
